org.itsnat.comp.list

Interface ItsNatFreeComboBox

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.awt.ItemSelectable, ItsNatComboBox, ItsNatComponent, ItsNatElementComponent, ItsNatFreeComponent, ItsNatFreeList, ItsNatList, ItsNatUserData

    public interface ItsNatFreeComboBox
extends ItsNatFreeList, ItsNatComboBox
    Is the interface of the free combo box components.

    ItsNat provides a default implementation of this interface.

    There is no default decoration of item selection, selection listeners (java.awt.event.ItemListener) may be used to decorate the item markup when its selection state changes.

    Author:
    Jose Maria Arranz Santamaria
